mber are the letters D U D E or dude. The letters stand for: Deposition, Uplift, Down cutting and Erosion.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6624678\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6624678\">\n\n<div class=\"VideoHero\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\">\n<meta content=\"Rim Walk West of Grand Canyon Village\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"Ranger-led walking tour from Bright Angel Trailhead to Maricopa Point with Ranger Dave.\" itemprop=\"description\"/>\n<meta content=\"T11M47S\" itemprop=\"duration\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/1F975F41-EBA5-5E3D-BBB084C892550715/grca-RimWalkFinalEdits2_splash.jpg\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/media/video/view.htm?id=1F975F41-EBA5-5E3D-BBB084C892550715\" itemprop=\"embedURL\"/>\n<meta content=\"2020-10-14 00:00:00.0\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/>\n<div class=\"VideoHero-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-big-play-centered vjs-16-9\" controls=\"\" height=\"264\" id=\"av_1F975F41EBA55E3DBBB084C892550715\" poster=\"/common/uploads/imr/park/grca//B4D864F6-0D67-ECCF-BC648C69AC90FE0C/B4D864F6-0D67-ECCF-BC648C69AC90FE0C-large.jpg\" preload=\"metadata\" width=\"640\">\n<source label=\"720p\" res=\"720\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/1F975F41-EBA5-5E3D-BBB084C892550715/grca-RimWalkFinalEdits2_1280x720.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"480p\" res=\"480\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/1F975F41-EBA5-5E3D-BBB084C892550715/grca-RimWalkFinalEdits2_854x480.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"360p\" res=\"360\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/1F975F41-EBA5-5E3D-BBB084C892550715/grca-RimWalkFinalEdits2_640x360.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"240p\" res=\"240\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/gr